# Py3Challenges
A collection of challenges for programming beginners.


## Installation
via pip:
```shell
pip3 install Py3Challenges -U
```


## Getting Started
Try this script:
```python
import Py3Challenges as Py3C
Py3C.getting_started()
# read the instructions in the terminal
```


